	<p style="text-align: justify">[2] United Nations Refugee Agency (UNHCR). Zamboanga Displacement Response. Infographic. October 28, 2014. </p>
	<p style="text-align: justify">[3] United Nations. Philippines: Bohol Earthquake Action Plan. October 2013. 
	<a href="http://www.humanitarianresponse.info">www.humanitarianresponse.info</a>. </p>
	<p style="text-align: justify">[4] Philippine Daily Inquirer. 1,500 families displaced by Mamasapano clash, says CHR. 5 February 2015. </p>
